My mistake @gentlementlegen I think this may have been me, still forming the habit
@jordan-ae variables don't play into it, the logger takes the log and creates 4 versions of it, one of them is `diff` which is how the bot comments most of the time.
```ts
await addCommentToIssue(context, log?.logMessage.diff as string);
```
is the correct pattern

